不是fcitx-qimpanel-configtool的问题，fcitx-config-gtk依然没字体设置选项
但是fcitx-config-gtk3是有字体设置选项的，奇怪的是fcitx-configtool在没装fcitx-qimpanel-configtool之前和fcitx-config-gtk一样，装了之后和fcitx-config-gitk3一样
就不能直接用配置文件配置字体吗？ 以后还是用fcitx-config-gtk3好了
--------------------------------------------------------------------
编译玩发现fcitx-configtool还是没有字体选项,询问了CSSlayer,发现装fcitx-qimpanel-configtool之后运行下fcitx-qimpanel-configtool,再运行fcitx-configtool就有字体选项了
----------------------------------------------------------------------
compile fcitx on lubuntu 17.04 because fcitx don't have font option on lubuntu
aptitude search fcitx|grep install
apt remove fcitx fcitx-pinyin

git clone https://github.com/fcitx/fcitx.git -b master
cd fcitx
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
sudo make install
sudo make unstall  if you want remove it

http://forum.ubuntu.org.cn/viewtopic.php?t=352738

some depend packages: extra-cmake-modules libgettextpo-dev doxygen libenchant-dev libxml2-dev libpresage-dev libqt4-dev libopencc-dev libgirepository libgirepository1.0-dev  gcc build-essential automake libxtst6 libxtst-dev xorg-dev gettext libtool intltool libgtk2.0-dev cmake libdbus-glib-1-dev libx11-dev libcairo2-dev libpango1.0-dev
